Description: Interface package for 'sala', the spatial network analysis library
    from the 'depthmapX' softwre application. The R parts of the code are based
    on the 'rdepthmap' package. Allows for the analysis of urban and
    bulding-scale networks and provides metrics and methods usually found within
    the Space Syntax domain.
